location.fullValue: The 1594 with 3 car garage Plan, Stone's Throw

data.description: Delightful two-story home with adorable front porch! Flowing, functional floorplan with separate living and family rooms and formal dining room. Kitchen has been updated beautifully, including newer cabinets, stainless steel farmhouse sink and appliances, darling backsplash and modern finishes, plus other thoughtful improvements throughout the home! Gorgeous LVP flooring with nice, natural tones throughout the main level and leading upstairs, with carpet in the bedrooms. Upstairs primary suite offers dual sinks, walk-in shower and walk-in closet! This home sits on a nice corner lot, with a modest front yard and fully fenced backyard. The roof and furnace are only 7 years old! Situated in a great neighborhood with shopping, restaurants, parks & more conveniently just minutes away. Plus, you're just around the corner from the elementary and middle schools, and within Union High School boundary. Plus, there is a 2.25% assumable VA loan option available! Ask your agent about it today!
